    <p>English is Canvas' language default, but you can choose to view the Canvas interface in another language. </p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> Instructors have the option to change the language preference for their courses. If you view a course where the instructor has made this change (most often for a foreign language course), the course language will override the language in your user settings.</p>
  </div>
</div>

